## 6. Records (Article 30)

Retention decisions are recorded in the Art. 30 record of processing
activities and reviewed at least annually.

## 7. Review

This policy is reviewed annually and immediately whenever new categories
of Personal Data are introduced or when supervisory-authority guidance
materially changes.

